1099
00:44:08,199 --> 00:44:16,280
It requires every metric to respond to one essential question.

1100
00:44:29,420 --> 00:44:34,780
Do the numbers still carry the meaning we say they carry?

1101
00:44:36,380 --> 00:44:40,619
If the answer is negative, the metric must be rejected.

1102
00:44:41,679 --> 00:44:46,539
No matter how exact or impressive it may seem.

1103
00:44:46,559 --> 00:45:01,800
