1127
00:48:39,199 --> 00:48:45,199
This usually happens when people do not fully agree on what they observe.

1128
00:48:45,199 --> 00:48:56,679
Concepts like user-friendliness or perceived reliability often fall into this category.

1129
00:48:56,679 --> 00:49:09,340
When consensus is weak, numbers cannot be assigned directly.

1130
