1133
00:49:20,920 --> 00:49:34,400
Participants express their opinion by choosing levels such as strongly agree or strongly disagree.

1134
00:49:34,400 --> 00:49:42,400
This does not produce exact numbers, but it captures direction and intensity of opinion.

